What is ReplicaSet ?

It is a better version of Replication Controller allows more flexible way to match pods it used Selectors and Lables for more efficciently to managing pods

Example:replicaset.yaml
Letâ€™s say you want always 3 NGINX pods running. You define a ReplicaSet like this:


apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: ReplicaSet
metadata:
  name: nginx-replicaset
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: nginx
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: nginx
    spec:
      containers:
        - name: nginx
          image: nginx:latest
